Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:29.28,Song,,0,0,5,,Watashi ga nanimonona no ka tte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.84,0:00:29.28,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For so long I \NDidn't know who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:32.05,Song,,0,0,5,,Utau koto wa nanina no katte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.28,0:00:32.05,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}What songs I sing \NAnd what songs I sang
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:37.92,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hito ha ai o kuretakatte shiritaku mo nai
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.05,0:00:37.92,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For long enough that the one offering love \NDoesn't want to know me now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:43.93,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo itamunara kono itaminara
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.92,0:00:43.93,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But even if you're getting hurt, \NEven if it hurts a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:50.40,Song,,0,0,5,,Mōsukoshi mōsukoshi itai gurai ga ī
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.93,0:00:50.40,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}In a little more, just a little more\NThis pain will turn to joy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:56.64,Song,,0,0,5,,Kirainara kirai to ima kotoba ni shite
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.40,0:00:56.64,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Say you hate me, say all you want\NYour words don't frighten me a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:01:02.45,Song,,0,0,5,,Mienai ashita o koko de owara sete
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.64,0:01:02.45,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Cause if you do, your tomorrow, \NUnseen before, will die for good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:08.95,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo an'nani aishita kon'nani aishiteru
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.45,0:01:08.95,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But how I loved you before,\NI love you now just as much
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:18.90,Song,,0,0,5,,{\fade(0,600)}Sono shiawase no hitotsude ī oboete ite
