Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.79,0:21:42.80,Song,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{きっとそうそうやって来る筈無い}And it won't be long before they come for me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:44.95,Song,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{救い無き砂上の僕は}I'm running helpless through the quicksand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:49.56,Song,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{瘡蓋剥がし遊ぶ}Playing with scabs, trying to peel them off
