Comment: 1,0:21:07.42,0:21:20.76,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}The heavy rain is over now, \NShadows have ceased to roam, \NEven summer itself has come to an end
Comment: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:20.76,Song,,0,0,5,,Ame wa yande ita kage to aruide ita natsu ga owatte ita
