Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That time, I saw it, clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this how Fushina has been seeing this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, what was it Fushina has been seeing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I manage to find my own path to that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the place you're aspiring for is, \NI want to climb there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:41.62,Song,,0,0,0,,{\q2\fade(900,900)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\shad3\blur0.5\4c&H837851&\b1\fnHitch Hike\fs65\pos(321.465,90)\3c&HD0BFA9&}Episode 18\N\N\N {\fs150}\NYuri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, that's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Though the data and specs explanation is still rather weak, \Nyou excelled in getting across the new pachislot aspirations{/glamour - no clue what he means}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're slowly starting to get a good hand.{/to become adroit in our trade - a figurative sense expression, literally "raise/enlargen your hand" that ginya takes literally}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the man should feed himself \Nwith his hand only, isn't that so?{Lit: After all, I intend to eat/make living with just one of my hands - I've no clue, unless this is a masturbation joke; he means "I only press pachislot buttons with one hand"???; okay, this word may also mean "spin the real" so it's clearly an intentional ambiguity}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But where's the fun in that, Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{She means }Ain't that nicer to have a girl do it for you?{Lit: Can't she do it? - I still play along my own line and hope they mean "can't a girl feed you" and not "can't a girl jerk you off"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see where this is going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In your case, it's Yuri{your partner is yuri}. Isn't it?{this whole scene is such intersection of intrigues that I'm not sure about anything at this point}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's someone Amy knows too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's one very adorable girl. \NRight, Editor{abbreviation of 編集長} Hino?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She's nice, alright, \Nbut you should still keep your work neat{/work accurately}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally! \NWell then, if you excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your article the other day \Nenjoyed a rather warm reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a little premature,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but here's a bonus!{/So I felt like giving you a bonus}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to treat her to some exquisite dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if you excuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sweet youth.{hope}{/he's at his prime...}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,True. I wonder when the days \Nof my sweet youth{/my own height of prosperity} will start too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy, why won't you make love to me then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Making little ones as a housewife \Nis not my thing.{Lit: I'm not getting married with wife and children}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Coach Akiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamoi speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about that coach affair \Nfrom your letter the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, I made up my mind to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to have bothered you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach went to all that trouble just for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya's stupid ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. It's one of those rare days I'm loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's your program{plans} for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an auspicious day on the horoscope{https://kotobanoimi.com/ohigaramoyoku-imi-1765 - I used this yet I'm still in doubt as to what it means}, and unfortunately{no clue why she says it this way, methinks whole line is a convoluted game of contradiction, where she uses explicitly polite code for saying explicitly rude things}, it would appear I have nothing else to occupy myself with.{lit: my body is vacant/empty/free as well - I hate this line at this point and just wanna get done with it}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go somewhere then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I consider this an invitation for a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish, M'Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:05:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been such a long time. \NGoing out for a date with Ginya like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, all you ever live for is pachislot, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you wanna go over there too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm sure we came to here before as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.{guess} Last time, \Nwe turned right on the corner here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, to the left, \Nthen the straight path and up the stairs, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! This way. \NYuri, here! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Returned to childhood already?{Lit: something like a kid already}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:06:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not supposed to escape by yourself{/alone whenever you feel like it}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here, here! Up here! Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going straight this way. \NThen, on the second corner, turn left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And after that, take another left turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Next would be acute right... \N- Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It fwies!{guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we riding next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ginya, maybe that's enough of amusements?{/we return from amuzement park(guess)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had some thorough fun already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, there's something \NI wanted to have a quick word about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanted to have a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,still be able to fight then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. It slipped my lips before I knew it.{/Sorry. I let it slip unknowingly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In that maze earlier, had you escaped in under 20 minutes, \Nwe'd have gotten a prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did you want a word about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That was underwhelming{/infuriating}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya kept running away alone, \Nfar ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that much of a big deal.{/You're exaggerating}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, that's what mazes are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just {because it was }in a maze, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that way we're both getting lost.{/it's written "the path of lost" - lit}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I take the other way on just one corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you can no longer wait for me,{I hope i got this right and she means they cannot wait and chase, but not "won't"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can no longer chase you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's Yuri acts somehow very odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya is the one acting odd here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. "Me."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, your coffee. \NBlack just like you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this thing you're writing? A novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the story about?{what kind of story}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Advancing steadily towards your dream? \NThat's such a cool idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My name - Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine is Kamoi Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're done polishing it, \Nlet me read it too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Albeit I haven't really written \Na terrible lot of anything yet. But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll become the very first fan of it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise then. \NThe very first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, \Nmy favorite Ginya is the one from those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely different person from now's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so! \NTotally odd!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe it really is so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because my old man
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,turned out to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In Slothium, I came across an unexpected trail to my father \Nbeing alive, though I've always been told he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad is still alive, you know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go meet him.{quoting myself from ep13 though now I hear "can't see him" which makes no sense}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who should go meet him, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help you with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad was alive and by all means well.{was doing well}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why are you telling me this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I signed in as a Slothium participant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Slothium?{\i0} \NWhat now? What is even this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The place where I fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That fighting too... \NJust what is this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya, what in the world are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In this Slothium place \Nthose called "Pachislot-Aristocrats{/nobles}" -
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the best of the best slotters, \Npicked from all over the country
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,risk their lives in fierce battles \Non secret arenas{/battlefields} of that institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm one of those fighting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, in that place \Nthere's a slotter under the name of Daiba Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is a wielder of an astonishing technique\Ncalled the Finger of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,have you ever been engulfed in this irresistible heat \Nstraight from the bottom of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- I—\N- For the first time in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,this heat is so intense in power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,From just watching Daiba press buttons, \Nmy heart heats up to red-hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to let it ignite{added to somehow justify the next line aside from it being AnJ reference}, \Nfighting Daiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To turn into the white ash{Lit: until I become snow-white}, \Nburn my everything fighting him!{I want to fight him fiercely/have a hot battle}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out you've been busting your chops \Nin some place I had no idea about, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:38.71,Song,,0,0,0,,Bronze-Silk Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh hell, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there! \NMaster, coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Otonashi Ginya, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.47,0:12:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me. \NMust be one of your acquaintances{But he certainly has some business with you}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Young, young man! \NYou sure take a good care for your body, don't you?{unsure, I just hear "good body"}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Please hold it to yourself! \NAnd firstly, pops, who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, my bad. \NI beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, nobody cares for my name \Nso people just call me Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor? Then, what is your business to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I didn't want anything in particular from you, \Nbut rather to just meet you and look with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of it as nothing more than a zany pops'{aged man's} whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "chun-chun" then "totin-toton" \Ninto "tsun-tsun," I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Just because you're young, doesn't mean \Nyou can make it through our world with determination alone!{it wouldn't be wrong to say I only heard "because young", "you cannot/should not" and "our world/society"}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I will bother you no more.{Lit: Did I make a hindrance/nuisance?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, master. Can I ask you to present this coffee \Nto the young man as a treat from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck was that pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder. Here, coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure filled it to the brink.{I've no clue why he says that but that can only be interpreted this way}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a {treat }coffee on another's expense. \NMake sure to drink with gusto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She was not feeling well, \Nso she called me earlier to ask for a day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked mighty healthy yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You told her, didn't you{I've no clue why this question pops up here, maybe it's "you said something rude to her again" or "did you want to talk to her"}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted Yuri to understand \Nwhy am I being the way I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, my conscience weighs on me \Nfor staying silent this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I'm playing my first one-on-one match \Nagainst a General.{unsure, maybe "my first battle for the General promotion"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't screw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya, I don't mean to reproach{attack} you \Nfor giving out{telling about} Slothium to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you did that \Nbecause you were concerned about Yuri's feelings.{ didn't you?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, we proceed to the match for General's title \Nbetween Otonashi Ginya and Kasai Hajime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope for a heated fight.{/let's have ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We meet again, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we proceed to fighting, \Nlet me tell you just one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The essence{unsure, it sounds like "in the end,"} of pachislot is probability and data. \NAnd, of course, the timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I succeed the current King on his post, I'll make sure to eradicate any counter-scientific tactics like that of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Slothium will become a ground of methodical battle, where you can only defeat an enemy with a logic-based strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting ahead of yourself!{that nonsense sounds like you haven't woken up properly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.61,0:14:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not losing today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my. Such a young man acting like an old guard, \Nrejecting the idea of a warrior that can lose.{I hope I got this right}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, we are ready to start the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Participants are invited to pick a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A youngster packed with energy{/lively ...} versus \Na veteran{experienced} professor. Which one you think will win?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Game start: 5 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,3, 2, 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even need to rely on arbitrary things \Nlike the ability to stop the reel on the right title{/adroit eyes}!{unsure, it's rather "because you depend on ..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be quiet, I'm doing the math{calculations}. \NThis condition is vital for approximating{/drawing closer} my ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, done! \NClick and click.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Calculated using maths!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In this life, there's nothing \Nstatistical math can't predict!{he says the opposite - "there are no things you can deduce with calculation" but makes no sense}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That is our Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If Daiba has God's Finger, \NKasai has God's Brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Think I'll lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Little do you know the Goddess of Victory favors{accompanies} me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah! \NYet another unscientific fallacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You've made it pretty far, haven't you{I hope she means progress in slothium and not smthng else abstract, like "went a long way"}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, as soon as the bonus game ends, \Nthe probability of the Gold Time starting...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's at it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,1/504 multiplied by 1/2, add 1/504.{I hope I got the arithmetic operations right, not that it matters anything}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This gives us...{in other words,}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! Math pays off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Put a strain on your head while still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:17:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially so while you're young! \NLest your brains go putrid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My very nature opposes the idea \Nof such man being worth of fighting Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Only God decides who is worth fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Shit! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it about your Goddess of Victory again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she happen to go out for refreshments today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You're so obnoxious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not used \Nto showing respect for elders, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear no regrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nailed it! \NThis marks the beginning of my catching up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As per my reckoning, the probability of Gold Time \Nstarting for you after this roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,equals zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the existence of a tactic surpassing the God's Brain \Nremains an obscurantist speculation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:18:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I depose Daiba and succeed him in King's seat, \NI will retrain you too, as a prominent prospect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I like it or not, it appears the old chap would end up being more worthy of fighting.{she just says "I think he looks more worthy" as if it doesn't contradict her previous statement is without a hint of coercion}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You should keep one thing in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The decisive factor, \Nunbound by any category of reckoning -
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the existence of genuine strong-willed people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Bonus Game is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Show up, Gold Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I told you - equals a plain zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But the problem is not even your usual \Nsuccession strategy.{/it can be alleviated/increased by excessive training. - unsure, sounds rather like "but it's not a problem of practice"}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya, I know rumors are not liable \Nto sprouting out of thin air.{I hate this line, I was looking for any other meaning but it's clearly "it's not gossip walking on its own" and I'm clueless what gossip he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a fluctuation in luck{/fluke}{I hope I got "nami" right}. \NWhen it goes up, I'll outstrip you in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluctuations are but artifices, produced by people collecting data, intended to explain statistical exceptions.{Lit: Waves are but products of manufacture of people gathering data from later - this one is even more senseless than the previous one}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, in a machine, merely picking random\Nnumbers indiscriminately, there's no place for fluctuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, that gap is nigh overwhelming now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you can't win with youth alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:19:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me one can secure the victory \Nwith just math{it's "probability" but that'd sound weird} and data analysis?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Base one's play{/Press buttons} on calculation alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.16,0:19:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You are dead wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Reducing pachislot to mere math and data?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, \Nwhy am I getting so excited about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! \NGold Time, begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some steaming nonsense!\NTo enter the Gold Time with such measly score{I hope it's "having earned that score" and if not I'm too tired to redo it}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense... Nonsense. Nonsense! \NIt's a lie. Just a lie... A lie, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:20:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This equation... With the equation for victory, \Nmy designs{/aspirations} are crumbling too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The insolence!{I hope it is not "Structure", yet if it is I can only guess why he screams that here} Otonashi's raw ability to stop the reel \Nis defying me blatantly{guess, I dunno why he screams meoshi for the second time there}! Show some respect for the elders!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:20.06,Song,,0,0,0,,Kasai Hajime\NOtonashi Ginya
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Processor Kasai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he made a typical mistake \Nof not trying to grasp pachislot past the surface level.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Whilst the insides of it \Ncan only be comprehended by senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How come... How could you win \Nwith just your youth and without pondering?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,'Tis what that Victory Goddess of yours is for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,0:20:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The one smiling down on me \Nain't no Victory Goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead, my own Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I won't have any regrets about it,{/I intend to not have ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.00,0:22:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind.
