Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.01,0:22:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.78,0:22:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.64,0:22:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wavering.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.20,0:22:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.62,0:22:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Parting{/Separation}
